# Hyprland Keybindings

## Application Launchers
- **SUPER + T** → foot (terminal)
- **SUPER + R** → rofi (launcher)
- **SUPER + B** → vivaldi (browser)
- **SUPER + E** → yazi (file manager)
- **SUPER + TAB** → missioncenter

## Window Management
- **SUPER + F** → fullscreen
- **SUPER + W** → kill active window
- **SUPER + SPACE** → toggle floating

## Screenshots & Media
- **SUPER + SHIFT + S** → screenshot
- **SUPER + PLUS** → volume up
- **SUPER + MINUS** → volume down
- **SUPER + RETURN** → mute system

## Music (YouTube Music)
- **SUPER + M** → play / pause
- **SUPER + ,** → previous
- **SUPER + .** → next

## Workspaces
- **SUPER + 1–5** → switch workspace

## Focus Movement
- **SUPER + ← / → / ↑ / ↓** → move focus

## Mouse Bindings
- **SUPER + MouseL** → move window
- **SUPER + MouseR** → resize window
